OL,3,CJersey Ministers consider standard
OL,4,Chourly rate for 'care at home'
OL,6,FJersey Ministers are proposing a new
OL,7,Fstandard hourly rate for domiciliary
OL,8,Fcare, following an independent market
OL,9,Freview.
OL,11,FWith an ageing population and the
OL,12,Fnumber of people needing long-term
OL,13,Fcare rising, ministers want to
OL,14,Fintroduce the hourly rate from 1
OL,15,FJanuary 2025.
OL,17,FUnder proposals, the rate will be
OL,18,F#34.80 with ancillary rates concerning
OL,19,Fcare that is not covered.
