OL,3,CJersey Ministers consider standard
OL,4,Chourly rate for 'care at home'
OL,6,FTo support existing claimants, ongoing
OL,7,Fcare packages charged above the new
OL,8,Fstandard rate will be honoured based
OL,9,Fon current fee rates for up to 2 years.
OL,11,FSome care providers, such as Adam
OL,12,FChamberlain from Orchid Care, says the
OL,13,Ftwo-year gap gives them time to find a
OL,14,Fworkable solution.
OL,16,FAdam says: "It's a case of 'let's see
OL,17,Fwhat we can do'. We need to work with
OL,18,Fthis.
